data.description: Come see this beautiful Colonial style home! This home offers 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths on the upper level as well as a half bath on the main floor. The kitchen has beautiful countertops as well as an island, giving you additional counter space. The back patio has a gazebo giving you a great place to sit and drink coffee while looking across a pasture that backs up to the property.
